Package: SVAlignR
Version: 0.4.6
Date: 2025-04-09
Title: Recovering Structure of Long Molecules from Structural Variation Data
Authors@R: person(given = c("Kevin", "R."), family = "Coombes",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "krc@silicovore.com")
Description: Implements a method to combine multiple levels of multiple
  sequence alignment to uncover the structure of complex DNA rearrangements.
